y \u2013 (4 years)<\/li>\n<li>Management \u2013(3 yrs)<\/li>\n<li>Business administration \u2013 (4 yrs)<\/li>\n<li>Interdisciplinary studies \u2013 (3 and 4 years)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"tuition-feesuniversite-de-hearst-undergraduate-programs\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tuition_FeesUniversite_de_Hearst_Undergraduate_Programs\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc79493785\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc79493260\"><\/a>Tuition Fees|Universit\u00e9 de Hearst Undergraduate Programs<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Tuition fees are $540 per 3-credit course. The tuition cost of full-time studies (30 credits) for the 2024-2024 school years is $5,400.<\/p>\n<p>For more information click <a href=\"http:\/\/www.uhearst.ca\/administration\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>See also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Universit\u00e9 de Hearst Undergraduate Programs \u2013Online Application for undergraduate, Universit\u00e9 de Hearst Application login, Application fees, Deadlines, Program&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1338,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[895],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1337"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1337"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1337\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/